{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ceee3f28c5","title":"忆秦嫩·爱山关","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a8cdb929d5","index":0,"year":1935,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"ceee3f28c5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"39fd7adceb","type":"paragraph","text":"忆秦嫩·爱山关","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"2dd7d4bab9","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年2月）西风烈，长空雁叫霜晨月。霜晨月，马蹄声碎，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"46777884a4","type":"paragraph","text":"喇叭声咽","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"f72d8f9ba6","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]娄山关，在贵州省第二大城市遵义城北娄山的最高峰上，是防守贵州北部重镇遵义的要冲。中央红军长征时，于1935年1月占领遵义，召开了在革命历史上有伟大意义的遵义会议。会后，红军经娄山关北上，原准备在泸州和宜宾之间渡过长江，没有成功，就折回再向遵义进军，在途中经半天激战打败了拒守娄山关的贵州军阀王家烈部一个师，乘胜重占遵义。这首词写的就是这次攻克娄山关的战斗。前阀写红军拥晓时向娄山关进军的情景；后冈写红军攻占和越过徒称天险的娄山关时，太阳还没有落山。词中的“西风”“雁叫”“霜晨”都是当地二月间的真实情景。毛泽东自注：“万里长征，千回百折，顺利少于困难不知有多少倍，心情是沉郁的。过了眠山，龄然开朗，转化到了反面，柳暗花明又一村了。以下诸篇（按：1958年出版的《毛主席诗词十九首》，《忆秦娥·娄山关》排在《十六字令三首》之前，“以下诸篇，指《十六字令三首》《七律·长征》《念奴娇·昆仑》《清平乐·六盘山》），反映了这一种心情。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"9f4c7c2e62","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]咽，在这里读入声。本义是声音因硬塞而低沉，这里用来描写在清雄关漫道真如铁，而今迈步从头越。从头越，苍山如海，","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"e6b6299599","type":"paragraph","text":"残阳如血。l[11从头越，重新跨越。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"ded1a5997c","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]苍山如海，残阳如血，据毛泽东说，是在战争中积累了多年的景物观察，一到娄山关这种战争胜利和自然景物的突然遇合，就造成了他自以为附录：1934年的原版本","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"d129fc1b73","type":"paragraph","text":"西风烈，梧桐叶下黄花发，黄花发，马蹄声碎，喇叭声咽。雄关漫道真如铁，而今迈步从头越。从头越，苍山如海，残阳如血。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"f8f6515158","type":"paragraph","text":"预湖内烧分点山和财高瑞护科利同西凤照明养平训京宝素一二","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"a81747e728","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"20b0208bb3","type":"paragraph","text":"加宝酒毛泽东写于1934年的《忆秦娥·娄山关》。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"aa2c7d4086","type":"paragraph","text":"汽","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"3df0e0d2a8","type":"paragraph","text":"中子立费山","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"759cbf9eec","type":"paragraph","text":"药锅","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"4c37709a18","type":"paragraph","text":"出店焦务","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"eb8b7b4784","type":"paragraph","text":"部","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"d403268576","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"45ad1d6c88","type":"paragraph","text":"汾8","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"39d6906f5b","type":"paragraph","text":"微","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"2a4d3054fd","type":"paragraph","text":"2毛泽东手书《忆秦·娄山关》","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"94f3390894","type":"paragraph","text":"中","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"57275518a2","type":"paragraph","text":"中港州路","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"ceee3f28c5"},{"id":"44b2871bf6","type":"paragraph